Revision history for Text-Shorten

0.06	2013-03-27
	Accomodate new, sometimes inconsistent hash ordering scheme in
	Perl 5.17.10

0.05	2012-06-07
	RT#77673 fix: iterating over hash resets 'each' iterator
	Pod and test improvements.

0.04	2011-07-08
	Bug fix in abbreviation routine for long hashes.

0.03	2011-02-16
	Efficiency improvements for arrays and hashes with thousands
	of elements.

0.02	2011-01-20
	Made compatible with <= v5.8.

0.01	2011-01-18
	First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
